# Testing Strategy

_Testing conventions and coverage targets._

## 1. Local Development Setup

1. Clone the repository
{%% if package_manager == "npm" %%}
2. Run `npm install`
3. Run `npm run dev`
{%% elif package_manager == "pnpm" %%}
2. Run `pnpm install`
3. Run `pnpm dev`
{%% elif package_manager == "uv" %%}
2. Run `uv sync --all-extras`
3. Run `uv run {= dev_command or "python -m app" =}`
{%% elif package_manager == "pip" %%}
2. Run `pip install -e ".[dev]"`
3. Run `{= dev_command or "python -m app" =}`
{%% elif package_manager == "go mod" %%}
2. Run `go mod download`
3. Run `{= dev_command or "go run ./cmd/server" =}`
{%% else %%}
2. _(Install dependencies)_
3. _(Start development server)_
{%% endif %%}

