## 4. Execution Evidence Rules

When running tests:
- Always show the exact command executed
- Always show the output including pass/fail counts
- Never claim tests pass without showing terminal evidence

## 5. Coverage Targets

- **Unit tests**: ≥ 80% for core modules
- **Integration tests**: Key user flows

